---
title: Teriyaki Chicken & Ginger Veggie Stir-Fry with Rapid Rice & Lime
description: Say hello to bold flavours and speedy cooking with this stir-fry spectacular! Juicy chicken, crisp veggies, and fragrant ginger sizzle in a glossy teriyaki glaze, all served over fluffy rice. It’s fresh, fast, and packed with deliciousness!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
